cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV) sub-categories as it deals with few-shot learning in image classification. It also involves the use of meta-learning, which is a popular topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Additionally, the optimization-based and metric-based approaches used in this paper are related to neural networks (cs.NE).
